OL,3,CBank of England could cut base rate if
OL,4,Cjobs market continues to slow ` Bailey
OL,6,FThe Bank of England could make cuts to
OL,7,Finterest rates if the jobs market
OL,8,Fslows down, Andrew Bailey has said.
OL,10,FBusinesses are "adjusting employment"
OL,11,Fas a result of Chancellor Rachel
OL,12,FReeves' decision to raise national
OL,13,Finsurance contributions (NICs) for
OL,14,Femployers, the governor of the Bank
OL,15,Falso told The Times.
OL,17,FCompanies are "also having pay rises
OL,18,Fthat are possibly less than they would
OL,19,Fhave been if the NICs change hadn't
OL,20,Fhappened", Mr Bailey said.
