OL,3,CBank of England could cut base rate if
OL,4,Cjobs market continues to slow ` Bailey
OL,6,FIn an interview with the newspaper,
OL,7,Fthe governor said the British economy
OL,8,Fwas growing behind its potential.
OL,10,FThis could open up "slack" to bring
OL,11,Fdown inflation, he said, meaning
OL,12,Fprices on goods would rise less
OL,13,Fswiftly compared with earnings in
OL,14,Ffuture.
OL,16,FMr Bailey said he believes the base
OL,17,Frate set by the Bank of England would
OL,18,Fbe lowered in future, after it was
OL,19,Fheld in June.
