OL,3,CBank of England could cut base rate if
OL,4,Cjobs market continues to slow ` Bailey
OL,6,FThe current Bank rate of 4.25%, which
OL,7,Fhas a bearing on all lending in the UK
OL,8,F` including mortgages ` will be
OL,9,Freviewed again on August 7 by the
OL,10,FBank's Monetary Policy Committee.
OL,12,F"I really do believe the path is
OL,13,Fdownward," Mr Bailey told The Times.
OL,15,FHe added: "But we continue to use the
OL,16,Fwords 'gradual and careful' because...
OL,17,Fsome people say to me 'why are you
OL,18,Fcutting when inflation's above
OL,19,Ftarget?'"
